column5: Please join me in congratulating JOEY   who's entry 'MISSION ACCOMPLISHED" will be used on our website. Joey will receive the very first 4 Torpedo Divers produced of our first production run. Thank you Joey!  As our way of saying THANK YOU to the rest of the participants,  ALL THOSE THAT PARTICIPATED ARE WINNERS!  We will ship* one Torpedo Diver to each person that posted an entry.  Please send us an email [emailÂ protected] and include your username and we will contact you when we have completed our first production run.  *Shipping costs not included.  Thank you Everyone For Your Participation,  Matthew
Congrats Joey!
congrats Joey...Now you and Paul can go down.  I kinda liked the logo gbfisher posted though, to bad it didn't stick around long.
Wow, that's super  Thanks so much!!!  Can't wait to use them Vanselena and give a full report about them.  Joey

great job n congrats Joey  and that was very nice and generous of you Vanselena  i'm very interested in your product so i'll be shooting over an email
As the big winner Joey will not be paying shipping
